Dialogue: 9,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.06,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:02.06,0:00:06.02,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{If this was going to happen, it'd have \Nbeen better if you had stayed distant!}Nếu mọi chuyện lại trở nên như vậy, thà anh hãy tạo khoảng cách với em đi!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.27,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{If you had...}Thà rằng như thế...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.78,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have realized my feelings for you,}Em đã không nhận ra tình cảm em dành cho anh...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.53,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{or been pained by those feelings \Nafter learning about Asuna-san...}hay đau khổ sau khi biết chuyện của Asuna-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.41,0:00:20.79,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have tried to forget about you \Nby falling in love with Kirito-kun, either!}Em đã không phải cố quên anh bằng cách đem lòng yêu Kirito-kun rồi!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.67,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Anh xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.30,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Just... leave me alone.}Xin anh... hãy để em một mình.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.87,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ever since that time,}Kể từ lúc đó...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:24.87,0:02:30.00,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I couldn't really understand my \Nrelationships, even within my family.}tôi nhận ra mình đã luôn tạo khoảng cách với mọi người, kể cả gia đình mình.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:31.71,0:02:35.38,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The fact that I wasn't actually a child of this family—}Sự thật là tôi không phải là con của gia đình này—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.93,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I realized this when I was ten.}Tôi biết điều đó khi vừa mới lên mười.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.40,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Who is she really?"}"Em ấy thật sự là ai nhỉ?"
Dialogue: 9,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.61,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Do I really know her?"}"Liệu mình có quen biết em ấy không?"{I know the "really" is repetitive, but the Japanese is repetitive too.}
Dialogue: 9,0:02:55.36,0:03:01.16,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe those unsettling feelings were one \Nof the reasons I turned to online games.}{This guy's so melodramatic sometimes...}Có lẽ cảm xúc bất an đó là một trong những nguyên nhân tôi bắt đầu chơi game online.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:02.66,0:03:07.58,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A fabricated world where nobody \Ntruly knows one another.}Một thế giới ảo nơi mà không ai biết rõ về người khác.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.92,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I indulged in the comfort of that world.}{Honestly, I think he just likes the feeling of power...}Tôi bắt đầu bị lôi cuốn vào sự tự do của cái thế giới ấy.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:13.58,0:03:17.92,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But the two years I spent in SAO \Nallowed me to discover a single truth}Nhưng sau hai năm sống trong SAO,\N tôi đã nhận ra rằng,{there's a difference between single and singular and considering he says "hitotsu no" I think you want "single"}{In terms of editing, "single truth" sounds better and is much more common than "singular truth"}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.43,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's essentially no difference between \Na real world and a virtual world.}Thế giới ảo và thế giới thực đều giống nhau.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.85,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's pointless to question who someone really is.}Hỏi một người thực sự là ai rất vô nghĩa.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:26.68,0:03:31.48,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All you can do is believe and accept.}Chúng ta chỉ có thể tin tưởng và chấp nhận nhau.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:31.48,0:03:36.36,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Because the way you perceive \Nsomeone defines their true self.}Bởi vì cách bạn thấu hiểu một ai đó nói lên tính cách thật sự của họ.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.65,0:03:43.53,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When I returned to the real world, \NI saw Sugu and was truly glad.}Khi trở về thế giới thật và nhìn thấy Sugu, tôi vô cùng hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.83,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I swore to myself}Tôi đã tự hứa với bản thân mình rằng...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:46.83,0:03:53.12,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{that I would close the gap that had grown \Nbetween us over the past few years.}tôi sẽ hàn gắn lại khoảng cách giữa hai anh em trong những năm qua.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.13,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{However, I...}Tuy vậy... nhưng...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.85,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What I can do for Sugu?}Mình có thể làm gì cho Sugu đây?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.60,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Sugu.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.10,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'll be waiting for you at the northern terrace of Alne.}Anh sẽ chờ em ở khu đất cao phía bắc Alne.{No... That's when you should face her in real life, no? This coward ==}{Wow... this guy. Still talking about the game even after everything that just happened?}
Dialogue: 9,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.62,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Despite all of the horrible things I said...}Mình đã nói bao nhiêu điều tệ mà ảnh vẫn...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.62,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{You're so strong, Onii-chan.}Anh mạnh mẽ thật đấy, Onii-chan.{Don't let that coward trick you, Suguuuu}
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.00,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I can't be as strong as you.}Em không thể mạnh mẽ như anh được.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.76,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Back then, I told you to keep trying,}Vào lúc đó em bảo anh hãy cố gắng lên...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.22,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{that you can't give up.}rằng anh không thể bỏ cuộc.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:44.22,0:04:47.97,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But now...I'm the one that's crying.}Thế mà bây giờ... mình chính là người đang khóc.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.12,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Still, what should I say...?}Dù vậy, mình nên nói gì đây...?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.92,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Leafa-chan!{Eww... it's the whiny kid.}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.84,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Jeez, I've been looking everywhere for you, Leafa-chan.}Thiệt tình, mình tìm bạn khắp nơi đó, Leafa-chan.{Even though she was offline? What?}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.60,SAO1,,0,0,0,,R-Recon?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.81,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Weren't you held captive by the Salamanders?}Không phải cậu bị bon Salamander bắt sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.56,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I poisoned them all and escaped.}Mình hạ độc bọn chúng xong rồi chuồn đó.{So convenient.}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.98,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Poisoned?}Hạ độc?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.90,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{And then, I came looking for you.}Và sau đó mình đuổi theo bạn.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.69,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Ờ mà...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.86,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{So, where's that Spriggan?}Anh chàng Spriggan đó đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.15,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Well...}Etou...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.95,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{You see, I said something terrible to him.}Cậu biết đó, mình có nói những điều không hay đến anh ta...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.83,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Something I really shouldn't have.}Những điều mà mình không nên nói.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.62,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'm such an idiot.}Mình quả thật là một con ngốc mà.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.88,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Sorry if I weirded you out just now.}Xin lỗi nếu như bây giờ làm cậu lúng túng nhé.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.80,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I won't be seeing him anymore.}Mình dự sẽ không gặp anh ta nữa đâu.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.01,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Let's go back to Swilvane.}Hãy về Swilvane cùng nhau nào.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.60,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Leafa-chan...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.68,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Leafa-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.98,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Leafa-chan, you can't cry!}Cậu không được khóc, Leafa-chan! {hell naw, don't you touch my sugu}
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.98,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}V-Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.15,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{The Leafa-chan I know should always be smiling!}Leafa-chan mà tui biết lúc nào cũng tươi cười cả!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.94,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I... I'll always be beside you!}M-Mình nhất định sẽ ở bên cạnh cậu mà!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.53,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Whether it's in the real world or \Nhere, I'll never let you be alone!}Cho dù có ở ngoài thế giới ảo này hay ở đâu đi nữa, mình sẽ không để bạn phải cô đơn đâu!{I'll never leave you alone!}{wahaha I just realized how that sounded after I typed it out. Well, it's true!}{This guy is such a creeper~}{For a less creepy alternative, "I'll make sure you're never alone!"}
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.53,0:06:28.95,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Hey—}Khoan đ—
Dialogue: 9,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.95,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I-I... Leafa-chan...}Leafa-chan... M-Mình....
Dialogue: 9,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.33,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Suguha-chan, I like you!}Suguha-chan, mình thích bạn!{NOOOO... REALLY?}{you're so dead, don't touch my sugu}
Dialogue: 9,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.66,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Um...}Anou...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.50,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wait! What do you think you're doing?!}Đợi đã! Cậu nghĩ cậu đang làm gì thế hả?!{okay, yeah, seriously. The dude went for the kiss? As sorry as I feel for him that was just stupid}{I WILL CHOP YOU}
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.59,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{A-Are you okay?}C-Cậu không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.59,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{That's weird.}Sao kỳ vậy.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:51.59,0:06:57.31,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{At this point, I thought it all depended on \Nwhether or not I had the courage to confess.}Cứ tưởng chỉ cần lấy hết can đảm mà tỏ tình thì nhất định sẽ thành công chứ.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.81,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{You're a real idiot, aren't you?}Cậu biết là cậu ngốc lắm không?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.65,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should learn a thing or two from you.}Nhưng có lẽ tớ cũng cũng học được một hai thứ từ cậu.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.72,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Nè.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.84,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Sorry for the wait.}Xin lỗi đã để anh đợi.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.39,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Sugu—
Dialogue: 9,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.56,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Onii-chan, let's have a duel.}Onii-chan, đấu nào.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.31,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{To finish what we started.}Hãy kết thúc nốt những gì còn dang dở.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.07,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{This time, there's no holding back.}Lần này anh không nhân nhượng nữa đâu.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.38,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{No wonder he looked so confident back then.}Thảo nào nhìn anh lúc đó hết sức tự tin.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.71,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Here I come!}Em tới đây!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.61,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Gì thế?{lol, why are they spinning? o___o}
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.20,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{How come?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.66,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to apologize to you,}Anh muốn xin lỗi em...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.41,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{but I didn't know what to say.}nhưng anh lại không biết nên nói gì.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.92,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{So I thought I'd do so by letting you strike me.}Nên anh nghĩ anh có thể xin lỗi bằng cách để em đánh anh.{I don't see how this is a viable solution... Too much forced drama}{maybe make it clearer... like "take it out on me" or something}
Dialogue: 9,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.05,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật sao?{Nope. He was genuinely surprised to see he didn't hack you into pieces with his first attack...}
Dialogue: 9,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.34,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Anh xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.01,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Me, too.}Cả em cũng vậy.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:41.18,0:09:47.06,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I haven't really returned from that world yet.}Anh vẫn chưa hoàn toàn trở về từ thế giới đó.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.11,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{It's still not over.}Mọi chuyện vẫn chưa kết thúc.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.78,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Until she opens her eyes, that world is my reality.}Cho đến khi cô ấy mở mắt thì thế giới đó vẫn là hiện thực đối với anh.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.99,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{So...}Vì vậy...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:56.45,0:10:01.12,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I don't know what to think of you yet.}Cho nên anh cũng không biết cảm xúc của anh dành cho em như thế nào nữa.{I'm sorry, but I really don't like how Kirito handles things... If he wasn't the main character he'd have run into so many bad ends with his indecisive behavior.}
Dialogue: 9,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.45,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'll be waiting.}Em sẽ đợi.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:05.45,0:10:10.08,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{For the time you finally come back home from that world.}Em sẽ đợi đến khi anh trở về từ thế giới đó.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.55,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Until then, let me help you!}Cho đến lúc đó, hãy để em giúp anh!{Kirito's sword warps in appearance in practically every episode. Sometimes it's longer, shorter, thinner, fatter, more triangular, less triangular, etc.}{uh... "foreshortening"?}
Dialogue: 9,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.81,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Um...}Etou...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.14,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's going on?}R-Rút cuộc mọi chuyện là sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.94,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{We're going to clear Yggdrasil.}Chúng ta sẽ phá đảo Yggdrasil.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:29.94,0:10:34.23,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{With the three of us: him, you, and me.}Chỉ với ba người chúng ta: anh ta, cậu và tớ.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.15,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I-I see.}H-Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.57,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?!}C-Cái gì?!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.24,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Yui, you there?}Yui con đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.49,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{What is it, Papa?}Có chuyện gì sao Papa?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.54,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Did you figure anything out during \Nthat fight with the guardians?}Con có nhận thấy điều gì trong lần trước đánh nhau với bọn lính gác đó không?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:48.54,0:10:53.96,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{In terms of stats, they're not particularly \Npowerful, but their numbers are overwhelming.|}Theo những gì con thống kê được thì bọn chúng không mạnh lắm nhưng mà số lượng lại quá áp đảo.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.96,0:10:58.17,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{It's almost as if the area is designed \Nto be impossible to overcome.}Cứ như thể cả khu vực thiết kế để không thể nào vượt qua được ấy ạ.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.93,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{So together, they're practically \Na massive, invincible boss, huh?}Vậy khi bọn chúng cùng nhau chiến đấu thì chúng là đối thủ khó xơi và quá đông sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:02.93,0:11:09.64,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{However, with Papa's skill proficiency, it may \Nbe possible to break through momentarily.}Tuy nhiên với kỹ năng chiến đấu của Papa thì có một tia hy vọng để vượt qua được chúng đấy ạ.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.10,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{You guys,}Mọi người...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:12.90,0:11:18.28,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but could you put up with \Nmy selfishness one more time?}Tôi xin lỗi, nhưng có thể nhờ mọi người giúp tôi đạt được sự ích kỷ của bản thân một lần nữa được không?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.61,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{For some reason, it feels like \Nwe're running out of time.}Vì một vài lý do nên thời gian của chúng ta không còn nhiều..
Dialogue: 9,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.83,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{If it's something I can do, you can count on me.}Nếu trong khả năng của em, anh cứ để em lo.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.33,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{And that goes for him, too.}Và cả cậu ta cũng vậy nữa.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.83,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Well, Leafa-chan and I are one \Nin body and soul, after all.}Dù sao Leafa-chan và tôi cũng hòa lại thành một cơ thể và tâm hồn rồi mà.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.46,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Don't get ahead of yourself!}Đừng có nói bậy bạ chứ!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.30,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Mình xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.22,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Let's do our best.}Cùng nhau cố gắng nhé.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.40,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Thanks, you two.}Cảm ơn hai người.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.74,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'll take on the guardians.}Bọn lính gác cứ để anh lo.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.49,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Staying back and healing me \Nshouldn't make them target you.}Cứ đứng sau lưng hồi máu thì chắc không nằm trong mục tiêu của bọn chúng đâu.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.37,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Let's go.}Đi thôi.{Dat BGM~}
Dialogue: 9,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.63,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wow.}Giỏi ghê.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.00,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{But there are too many!}Nhưng bọn chúng đông quá!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.15,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{There's no end to them.}Bọn này đông như kiến ấy.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.16,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Recon!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:33.16,0:13:33.83,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.67,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why are they targeting us?}Tại sao bọn chúng cũng nhằm vào chúng ta luôn kìa?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.67,0:13:50.47,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Their AI probably runs on different \Nalgorithms than other monsters.}Chắc AI của bọn chúng được lập trình khác với bọn quái thông thường.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.10,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{In that case, it's meaningless to divide roles.}Trường hợp này chúng ta ai cũng như ai thôi.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:57.27,0:13:57.94,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.44,SAO1,,0,0,0,,Recon?!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:00.90,0:14:07.91,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Leafa-chan, I don't really understand, \Nbut this is important, right?}Leafa-chan, mình không hiểu cho lắm, nhưng chuyện này với cậu rất quan trọng đúng không?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.07,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.08,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{It's probably not just a game.}Có thể đây không còn là một trò chơi nữa.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.79,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Not now, that is.}Hiện tại thì là như thế.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.00,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{I'll do something about it!}Vậy hãy để đó cho mình!{Fail please.}
Dialogue: 9,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.42,SAO1,,0,0,0,,R-Recon?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.85,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Y-You idiot!}C-Cái tên ngốc này!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.56,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no.}Chết rồi.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.79,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Recon, that's enough. Run outside!}Recon đủ rồi, mau chạy đi!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.97,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{That's... dark magic.}Đó là... phép thuật hệ bóng tối.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.57,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Self-destruction magic?}Phép tự kích nổ sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.49,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{The death penalty for that is pretty serious...}Hình phạt cho phép đó rất nặng đó...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.87,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{You really are an idiot!}Cậu đúng là đồ ngốc mà!{Now if only they communicated and timed it >_>}{Yes! He failed!}
Dialogue: 9,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.06,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{No way.}Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.94,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{No way... That's too much.}Không thể nào... Không được đâu...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.74,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{This is...}Cứ đà này...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.61,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{This is just...}Cứ đà này thì...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.55,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{The Sylphs?}Tộc Sylph?{lol, I totally forgot about them}
Dialogue: 9,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.18,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Nhưng mà tại sao?
